{"tid":1668230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌咁咪撐維吾爾人同加泰一個集會 瀨尿牛丸囉屌","createTime":"2019-10-22T01:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T01:32:43.000Z","uid":110109,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"af27257be7e8a50663af3adac0c96565d5bd680d","tid":1668230,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:21:07.000Z","msg":"又喺到玩埋啲命題 獨立唔獨立<br />\n四個月喇仲有潔癖你死撚左佢啦<br />\n<br />\n我地爭取係自由民主<br />\n自由民主唔係共產黨恩典或者佢哋施捨比我地先有<br />\n<br />\n冇自決（唉屌唔用獨立呢隻字喇）<br />\n邊個可以保你平安？<br />\n<br />\n依家加泰也好、新疆也好、香港也好<br />\n就係差一樣嘢 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">命運自主<br />\n<br />\n溝埋一齊搞<br />\n美歐唔會出聲喇掛？大義凜然喇掛<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n成班on9地圖都未識背喺到懶識國際關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64d5b9c387f5fa2ad96532624d1ab52332bbda3","tid":1668230,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:21:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b688394fa76bc0bbdfd5b2088e43b16cbc18c5a5","tid":1668230,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965c193ab935f4114739ef4006d040c15498cc6a","tid":1668230,"uid":110109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:25:47.000Z","msg":"既然集會已經申請左<br />\n咁想補飛<br />\n<br />\n大會或者有心人<br />\n咪好似1020咁印啲支持維族口號囉<br />\n<br />\n如果你又潔癖覺得東突旗=恐怖份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca384e4dd5d738ac76596d969fa6c3cd56ad1a28","tid":1668230,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:26:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd215a036033df161d2ab59724abd68d0720afc0","tid":1668230,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T01:28:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid